---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from "../consts";
import RecentPublications from "../components/RecentPublications.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body class="w-full max-w-screen-md mx-auto my-4 dark:bg-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300" >
    <Header />
    <main class="flex flex-col justify-center">
      <div class="px-4 md:px-16 flex flex-col gap-4 md:my-10">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl w-full">🧑‍🚀 Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
        <p class="w-full text-justify text-base md:text-lg">
          This is my evolving space—a place where I explore ideas, document thoughts, and refine what I’m learning over time. It’s not a traditional blog but a living, interconnected system of notes that shift and expand as I do.
        </br>
          What You’ll Find Here 
          I write and reflect on a range of topics, including:
          <ul>
            <li>
              🌟 Northstar – Core guiding principles and big-picture thinking
            </li>
            <li>
              💭 Reflections – Personal insights, life lessons, and musings
            </li>
            <li>
              📚 Bookshelf – Notes and takeaways from books I’m reading
            </li>
            <li>
              🛐 Faith – Faith, meaning, and deeper questions
            </li>
            <li>
              👥 Leadership – Management, decision-making, and influence
            </li>
            <li>
              ⚡ Productivity – Systems, habits, and efficiency
            </li>
            <li>
              ✈️ Travel – Thoughts and experiences from the road
            </li>
            <li>
              🎨 UX – Design, strategy, and user experience
            </li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      </div>
	  <RecentPublications />
	      </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

